g.text: Find and lease an apartment online with ease
Find an apartment he trusts and feels safe throughout the process
Avoid exess fees to be able to shop around for apartments
Pay his rent and be aware of when his roommate has paid
Hates keeping track of all of the units he has contacted
Feels comfortable contacting his property manager for assistance
Raymond is a developer who lives in Arizona but recently accepted
a job in Seattle. He needs to find an apartment he can trust
without ever viewing the unit (because of the distance).
He needs to be able to apply to multiple units and feel secure that
one of them will work out.
